wiki.summary: The song features production from French electronic duo Daft Punk, and is the second collaboration between The Weeknd and Daft Punk following Starboy, which was released earlier in 2016. It is taken from The Weeknd’s third studio album Starboy, released November 25th, 2016. Notable cover versions include: Celestial Aeon Project: I Feel It Coming - instrumental on Spotify Read more on Last.fm.
